      "type": "html",
      "text": "\nAccumulate a collection of such goals to apply the new language to (see [[Programming Chrestomathy]] for a few starters). Each one illuminates the language from a different angle. Seeing the same program - <i>writing</i> the same program - in different languages brings commonalities and differences between them into relief; different programs bring out different contrasts. (Meanwhile, your understanding of the original goal is deepening as each program is a reflection of <i>that</i> from different angles - and that deeper understanding can then feed back into how you write the programs.)",
